nsson was born in New York City. Her father, Karsten Johansson, is a Danish-born architect, and her paternal grandfather, Ejner Johansson, was a screenwriter and director. Her mother, Melanie Sloan, a producer, comes from an Ashkenazi Jewish family from the Bronx. Johansson has an older sister, Vanessa, who is an actress; an older brother, Adrian; a twin brother, Hunter (who appeared in the film Manny & Lo with Scarlett); and a half-brother, Christian, from her father's re-marriage.","popularity":17.177146,"place_of_birth":"New York City, New York, USA","profile_path":"\/8EueDe6rPF0jQU4LSpsH2Rmrqac.jpg","adult":false,"imdb_id":"nm0424060","homepage":null}